WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Across floating islands… a world still breathing.

00:07.000 --> 00:12.500
In the Hatchery, a Rift egg waits for a Keeper.

00:12.500 --> 00:18.000
Crack the shell. Meet your Riftling.

00:18.000 --> 00:24.500
Step into the Live World — explore regions, meet others, find your path.

00:24.500 --> 00:29.500
Talk to NPCs. Accept quests. Follow the trail.

00:29.500 --> 00:34.500
Train in battles. Test your bond.

00:34.500 --> 00:38.500
Craft gear. Shape what you need.

00:38.500 --> 00:42.500
Make a home. Rest with your companion.

00:42.500 --> 00:47.500
Join guilds. Celebrate events together.

00:47.500 --> 00:52.500
Trade in the player economy — build your own loop.

00:52.500 --> 01:00.000
Riftwilds. A browser fantasy multiplayer game.
Play the alpha. Enter the Live World.
